text.data-name: Navigate to the receivable module (from the home page of the main menu).
text.tspan: Navigate to the receivable module (from the home page of the main menu).

text.data-name: From the list, select the customer who is making the payment and tap “ Add Transaction”.
text.tspan: From the list, select the customer who is making the payment and tap “ Add Transaction”.

text.data-name: Enter the amount paid and for which service the payment is being made.
text.tspan: Enter the amount paid and for which service the payment is being made.

text.data-name: A customer receipt can then be generated from the Transaction Tab.
text.tspan: A customer receipt can then be generated from the Transaction Tab.

text.data-name: Meter readings take place towards the end of the month.
text.tspan: Meter readings take place towards the end of the month.

text.data-name: Go to the bank deposit module on the plant section of Home Page.
text.tspan: Go to the bank deposit module on the plant section of Home Page.

text.data-name: The meter reading page itemises the number of pending readings for each plant.
text.tspan: The meter reading page itemises the number of pending readings for each plant.

text.data-name: Select the In Hand cash tab.
text.tspan: Select the In Hand cash tab.

text.data-name: Access a specific customer account page through the customer list module.
text.tspan: Access a specific customer account page through the customer list module.

text.data-name: Click the pencil icon next to the relevant section.
text.tspan: Click the pencil icon next to the relevant section.

text.data-name: The customer may have to confirm the update through an OTP.
text.tspan: The customer may have to confirm the update through an OTP.

text.data-name: Navigate to the receivable module and select the plant.
text.tspan: Navigate to the receivable module and select the plant.

text.data-name: Customers are listed along with the amount owned.
text.tspan: Customers are listed along with the amount owned.

text.data-name: The field agent can sort the list in descending size of bill to prioritise customers.
text.tspan: The field agent can sort the list in descending size of bill to prioritise customers.

text.data-name: Selecting a plant will show a list of meters to be read.
text.tspan: Selecting a plant will show a list of meters to be read.

text.data-name: The amount collected and deposited in the billing period will be shown, along with the amount of undeposited cash held locally.
text.tspan: The amount collected and deposited in the billing period will be shown, along with the amount
of undeposited cash held locally.

text.data-name: Field agents must implement service requests, package changes, meter releases etc.
text.tspan: Field agents must implement service requests, package changes, meter releases etc.

text.data-name: To assign such a task to a particular agent, go to that task’s page and select the “pending” tab.
text.tspan: To assign such a task to a particular agent, go to that task’s page and select the “pending” tab.

text.data-name: From the list of pending tasks, locate the one you wish to assign and tap its “re-assign” button.
text.tspan: From the list of pending tasks, locate the one you wish to assign and tap its “re-assign” button.

text.data-name: The field agent may then be elected from a list of available agents. They will be automatically notified of the assignment, and can be contacted through the app for clarification.
text.tspan: The field agent may then be elected from a list of available agents. They will be automatically
notified of the assignment, and can be contacted through the app for clarification.

text.data-name: Readings can then be added to each meter.
text.tspan: Readings can then be added to each meter.
